'''伯多祿·帕羅林'''（{{lang-it|Pietro Parolin}}；{{bd|1955年|1月17日}}）是[[意大利|意大利]]籍[[天主教會|天主教會]][[樞機|樞機]]，2013年10月15日起擔任[[聖座|聖座]][[國務樞機卿|國務樞機卿]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://it.radiovaticana.va/news/2013/08/31/il_papa_nomina_mons._pietro_parolin_nuovo_segretario_di_stato/it1-724390 |title=Il Papa nomina Mons. Pietro Parolin nuove segretario di stato |publisher=[[Radio_Vaticana|Radio Vaticana]] |language=it |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2013-08-31 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212112903/http://it.radiovaticana.va/news/2013/08/31/il_papa_nomina_mons._pietro_parolin_nuovo_segretario_di_stato/it1-724390 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[教宗方济各|教宗方济各]]於2014年2月22日將他擢升为枢机<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/list-of-19-new-cardinals-named-by-pope/1828397.html |title=List of New Cardinals Named by Pope Francis |work=VOA |date=2014-01-12 |accessdate=2015-09-27 |language=en |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214602/http://www.voanews.com/content/list-of-19-new-cardinals-named-by-pope/1828397.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

